paragraphs.title: overall scores from result
paragraphs.text: %sql select _2, count(1) as overall from overall where _2 <= ${choose the maxi value} AND _2 >= ${choose the mini value} group by _2 order by _2

paragraphs.title: pronunciation scores
paragraphs.text:
%sql select _2, count(1) from pronunciation where _2<100 AND _2>0 group by _2 
order by _2

paragraphs.title: integrity scores
paragraphs.text:
%sql select _2, count(1) from integrity where _2<100 AND _2>0 group by _2
order by _2

paragraphs.title: fluency scores
paragraphs.text: %sql select _2, count(1) from fluency where _2<100 AND _2>0 group by _2 order by _2

paragraphs.title: accuracy/Dependence scores
paragraphs.text: %sql select _2, count(1) from accuracy where _2<100 AND _2>=0 group by _2 order by _2
